  "prompt": "Where can I get best quality Build In Wardrobes in Guildford?",
  "response": "If you're looking for high-quality built-in wardrobes in Guildford, there are several places you can consider:\n\n1. **Local Furniture Stores**: Visit local furniture stores that specialize in custom designs. They often have showrooms where you can see examples of their work.\n\n2. **Independent Craftsmen**: Look for local carpenters or joiners who can provide bespoke solutions tailored to your needs. Personal recommendations and online reviews can help you find reliable professionals.\n\n3. **Interior Design Companies**: Some interior design firms offer custom furniture services, including built-in wardrobes. They can provide a comprehensive service from design to installation.\n\n4. **Online Platforms**: Websites like Checkatrade, Houzz, or Rated People allow you to find and compare local tradespeople based on reviews and ratings. \n\n5. **Big Retailers**: While not always bespoke, larger retailers like IKEA, B&Q, or John Lewis offer a range of built-in wardrobe options that can be customized to some extent.\n\n6. **Showrooms**: Visit home improvement shows or design fairs in and around Guildford, where you can meet suppliers and see their offerings in person.\n\nEnsure you review portfolios and get quotes from multiple providers to compare costs, materials, and options before making a decision.",
